oracle.pg.text

Class OracleIndexParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.pg.text.OracleIndexParameters
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OracleTextIndexParameters

    public class OracleIndexParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages relevant parameters for text indexing. Such parameters include the Search engine (SolrCloud, Lucene) used, batch size, commit size, and degree of parallelism (DOP).
